Setup an local environment

1. Setup the environment
    Using docker, run the docker compose using the file "docker-compose.yml"
2. Create the data structure in elasticsearch
    Configure de connection with elasticsearch in "Mapping.py" and run the python script
3. Save issues in elasticsearch
    Change setting in "SaveIssues.py" and run the python script
4. Create the data sources in grafana
    "BT-ClosingDate" - index "projects_issues", Time field "closing_date"
    "BT-CreationDate" - index "projects_issues", Time field "creation_date"
    "BT-Projects" - index "projects", Time field "last_update"
5. Import dashboard ("grafana.json") to grafana
